text: Zumbrota may refer to: == Places == === United States === *Zumbrota, Minnesota, a city **Zumbrota Covered Bridge, Minnesota's last remaining covered bridge *Zumbrota Township, Goodhue County, Minnesota == Ships == *USS Zumbrota (YP-93), a patrol craft that served in the United States Navy from 1917 to 1923
